Also - if you think this might help others - I've found it very useful to change the "View pdf with Preview" script to be:\
\
--AppleScript direct\
\
tell application "Preview"\
 activate\
 open POSIX file #PDFPATH#\
end tell\
tell application "System Events" to tell application process "Preview"\
 click (menu item "Contact Sheet" of menu "View" of front menu bar)\
end tell\
