The extra System Events scripting has the annoyance of needing the Accessibility permission to be granted and will probably break for non-English users, but it opens Preview in Contact Sheet mode which I find very helpful for looking at the overall pagination of a document. Clicking on a thumbnail within Preview then opens that page in normal view so it's easy to "zero in" on some layout issue.\
